In re Resignation of Spencer.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Spencer (1991), 62 Ohio St.3d 1207.]

(No. 91-1948 Submitted October 9, 1991 Decided October 10, 1991.)

The resignation of Richard F. Spencer, Jr. as an attorney, Registration No. 0034179, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
